data.description: This home's location overlooking the first hole of the Ballantrae Golf Club provides scenic views and easy access to the golfing amenities.  High ceilings contribute to a sense of openness and grandeur within the home, creating an inviting atmosphere.  The presence of a gourmet kitchen featuring granite countertops suggests a high-end and stylish culinary space.  Fireplaces in two different areas provide both warmth and a cozy ambiance, making the home comfortable and inviting.  The main level master suite offers convenience and luxury, catering to a comfortable lifestyle.  The presence of a guest suite on the second floor ensures privacy and a separate living space for guests.  Every room features custom plantation shutters.  Overall, this property offers a combination of luxury, functionality, and a prime location for golf enthusiasts. This home is an ideal residence for those seeking a high-quality living experience in a beautiful setting.
